<TEXTAREA wrap=hard NAME="comment" ROWS="30" COLS="72" >Miniel＠EMさんは No.518「Cerulean　Armor」で書きました。
>KaelのRobe売ってるVenderがいるAreaの建物にいるTrainerからStartです。
>
>You say, 'hail Slaggak the Trainer'
>
>Slaggak the Trainer says 'Hello there, Troll. I am Slaggak, the 
>trainer.  The Kromrif here will soon be ready to serve the great and 
>honorable King Tormax. 
>
>You say, 'I will serve'
>Slaggak the Trainer says 'So you say, little one.  Why are you here, 
>then?  You should be out slaying those pestering little Coldain or 
>maybe those damnable shard wurms and wyverns. 
>
>You say, 'what is shard wurms and wyverns?'
>Slaggak the Trainer says 'You must have seen the shard wurms by now!  
>The lizards that roam the lands eating whatever they can find?  They 
>can grow to be quite ferocious!  Not nearly as ferocious as their 
>ancient cousins, the dragons, but a nuisance nonetheless.  We have a 
>bounty on those beasts here in Kael Drakkel. 
>
>You say, 'what is bounty?'
>Slaggak the Trainer says 'If you think you have what it takes to slay 
>the shard wurms or their relatives, the wyverns, bring back proof of 
>your exploits.  For every four shard wurm teeth you bring me, I am 
>authorized to reward you with a pair of cerulean greaves.  Every 
>fourth ice wyvern stinger will grant you a pair of vambraces. 
>
>CSのWyvernからIce Wyvern　Stingerを４本集めて渡します.
>
>Slaggak the Trainer says 'You are truly a worthy little Troll.  I 
>hope this armor serves you well.  If it does not, I am sure a 
>mercenary such as yourself could find a buyer. 
>Your faction standing with Kromrif got better
>Your faction standing with Kromzek got better
>Your faction standing with Coldain got worse
>Your faction standing with ClawsofVeeshan got worse
>You gain experience!!
>
>報酬としてCerulean　Vambraceが貰えます.
>MAGIC　slot:ARM
>AC11 STR2 Wt3.5
>Class:WAR CLR PAL SHD BRD  Race:ALL
>
>見た目緑色っぽいPlateでした。
>GreaveはまだやってないのでLOG同じになるかわかりません…
